Jane Chika Oranika (amụrụ Maachị 9, 1997),  amara aha ya dika Chika (nke a na- emebu CHIKA ), bu onye ọgụ egwu rap nke Amerika
O buru ụzọ dọta uche na mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta tupu ịbanye na Warner Records na 2019
N'afọ sochirinụ, etinyere ya na Klas Freshman nke XXL ' 2020 wee họpụta ya maka ihe nrite Grammy maka onye nka ọhụụ kacha mma(Grammy Awards for the Best New Artist
A mụrụ Chika na Montgomery, Alabama
N'ihi mmasị o nwere na egwu na uri slam, ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Booker T
Washington Magnet
A nabatara ya na kọleji Berklee a ma ama, ma n'ihi ọṅụ ego ụgwọ akwụkwọ,kama  ọ debanyere aha na Mahadum South Alabama
Ọ kwụsịrị mgbe afọ mbụ ya gachara ilekwasị anya na ọrụ egwu
Chika buru ụzọ nweta nlebara anya zuru ebe niile na-eso mgbasa ozi Instagram site n'abali itoolu nke ọnwa Nọvemba nke afọ 2016,  mgbe ntuli aka onye isi ala United States 2016 gachara

Na vidiyo ahụ, ọ na-ekpuchi onwe ya na mmalite ya, na-ekwu "African-American? Ọ dịtụghị mgbe ọ na-eche nke ahụ, anụtụbeghị banyere ya, ọ dịghị mgbe ọ detụrụ ya ire, ọ dịghị mgbe ọ sitere nka n'isi" Na mbido 2017, o mepụtara #EgoChallenge, na-eji abụ Beyoncé nke aha ahụ iji kwalite ịdị mma nke ahụ na ịhụ onwe ya n'anya
N'afọ ahụ ọ wepụtakwara ihe ngosi nganga -themed remix nke Ed Sheeran 's " Shape of You "
N'abalị anọ n'ọnwa Jun nke afọ 2017 o wepụtara EP nke dịịri onwe ya nke a na-akpọ Full Bloom
N'afọ 2018, Chika pụtara ìhè maka freestyle ekwupụtara Kanye West n'elu West nke " Jesus Walks " kụrụ
freestailụa metụtara nkwado West maka Donald Trump wee dọta uche nke Jada Pinkett Smith, Sean "Diddy" Combs, na Erykah Badu
O mechara wepụta freestailụ  onyefere Nia Wilson
N'ọnwa ọgọstụ 2018, o gosipụtara na egwu Rachel Crow "Coulda Told Me"
Chika wepụtara otu mpụta mbụ ya, "No Squares", na Eprel 2019
N'ọnwa na-esonụ, na òkù nke onye ọbịa Lena Waithe, ọ rụrụ dị ka "Richey v
Alabama", egwu ya ọzọ, na Jimmy Kimmel Live!
Egwu ahụ gbasara  Alabam 2019 abortion bill wee soro aha  enyi Chika gụọ ya aha
N'oge okpomọkụ ahụ, ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta nke Warner Records
Chika weputara alụlụ abụọ ọzọ dị ka onye na-edu ndú na 2019: "High Rises"   na "Enweghị ike ịkọwa ya" nke gosipụtara Charlie Wilson
N'afọ ahụ, ọ pụtakwara na JoJo 's " Sabotage ", nke ruru nọmba 18 na Billboard US R&B Digital Downloads
N'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2019, Chika kwupụtara na ya na-arụ ọrụ na mpụta mbụ nke mgbalị ihe omume akpọrọ Industry Games
N'abali iri abụọ na atọ nke ọnwa Jenụwarị afọ 2020, Chika kwadoro aha ya wee bipute snippets nke egwu sitere na EP, na-agwa ndị na-eso ụzọ na mwepụta ahụ bụ ọnwa abụọ
O weputara aha otu EP a na abalị iri na asatọ nke ọnwa Febrụwarị
E wepụtara EP a na ọnwa Machị 12, 2020
Na Ọgọstụ 11, 2020, Chika gụnyere na Klas Freshman nke XXL ' 2020
A họpụtara ya maka ihe nrite Grammy maka onye nka ọhụụ kacha mma
na ihe nrite onyonyo NAACP maka onye nka ọhụụ pụtara ìhè
N'abalị iri na otu nke ọnwa Maachị afọ 2021 Chika kwupụtara na a ga-ewepụta EP nke abụọ ya ozugbo n'oge oge n'etiti abalị

N'abalị iri nke ọnwa Epre afọ 2021, Chika biputere akwụkwọ mgbasa ozi ọha na eze na akaụntụ Twitter ya na-akọwa mkpebi ya ịla ezumike nká n'egwu mgbe ọ na-atụgharị uche na "mmetụta uche" ndụ dị ka onye na-akụ egwu na nchapụta emetụtala ahụike ya

Na nnọkọ Instagram Live nke ya na ndị Fans na-emekọrịta ihe na-eso ọkwa ezumike nka mbụ ya, ọ katọrọ itughari okwu bụ"trolls" ma ọ bụ "stans" bụ ndị "na-eche n'elu nsogbu uche ndị ọzọ na-eme ka ha ka njọ." Ọ kpọtụrụ aha kpọmkwem mmetụta nke mmetọ ịntanetị na ọgụ ya na-aga n'ihu na ịda mbà n'obi na mkpebi ya, n'agbanyeghị na ọ hapụrụ obere ohere maka nlọghachi na nkwupụta ikpeazụ ya
Chika nwetara ọrụ dị ka nwa akwụkwọ sekọndrị na 2020 Netflix Original ihe nkiri akpọrọ Ike Project Power
O nyekwara aka na afare  egwu "My Power"
Na Mee 2019, Chika gosipụtara na mgbasa ozi Calvin Klein #MyCalvins,  na-edekwa abụ maka mkpọsa S/S 2019
N'otu afọ ahụ, ọ sonyere dị ka ndị isi na Business of Fashion na Paris Fashion Week ma eseere ya mkpuchi ihu akwụkwọ ọnwa Decemba nke Teen Vogue
Azụmahịa nke Ejiji matara ya dị ka otu n'ime mmadụ Narị ise kachasị na-achikota ụlọ ọrụ ejiji na 2019
Chika bụ ọdụdụ nwa n'ime ụmụ nwanyị atọ nne na nna ya bụ ndị Naijiria na Amerika
O sitere n'agbụrụ Igbo wee zụlite ya n'okwukwe Pentikọstal
Chika na-akọwapụta dị ka nwoke na nwanyị na- enwe mmekọahụ ma na-ekwu banyere mmekọahụ na egwu na vidiyo ya
Na vidiyo ya maka "Enweghị ike ịkọwa ya", o tinyere ntụgharị nke ya na  A different world, otu n'ime sitcoms kachasị amasị ya
N'abalị iri atọ nke ọnwa Mee afọ 2020, ndị uwe ojii kpọchiri Chika obere oge na ngagharị iwe Los Angeles na-esochi ogbugbu ndị uwe ojii gburu George Floyd
O kwuru okwu ahụ merenụ na mgbasa ozi ọha na eze n'echi ya, na-ekwusi ike na udo dị na ngosipụta ahụ tupu itinye aka ndị uwe ojii
